325
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:30,310
You have to go.

326
00:15:30,350 --> 00:15:31,470
This is such a rare chance.

327
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:33,110
Director Stephen's movies

328
00:15:33,110 --> 00:15:34,430
are both profitable and artistic.

329
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,830
They are fast-selling and
award-winning movies.

330
