work with him, right?

332
00:15:38,510 --> 00:15:38,990
No.

333
00:15:39,230 --> 00:15:40,110
I can handle other things.

334
00:15:40,150 --> 00:15:41,390
But this...

335
00:15:42,590 --> 00:15:43,270
What do you mean?

336
00:15:44,710 --> 00:15:45,390
What I mean is,

337
00:15:46,630 --> 00:15:47,350
I think I have to

338
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:48,790
