339
00:15:49,190 --> 00:15:49,350
Think...

340
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:53,630
Are you okay?

341
00:15:53,670 --> 00:15:54,860
This is a great chance.

342
00:16:03,870 --> 00:16:04,630
Miss Yu.

343
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:07,070
You are Xiao Yi's friend, right?

344
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:08,790
Yes.

345
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:12,670
Are you working in
the entertainment industry too?

346
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:14,070
No.

347
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:31,470
I'll get the door.

348
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:57,990
[Door is opened.]

349
00:17:00,390 --> 00:17:01,030
Where's Xiao Yi?

350
00:17:01,950 --> 00:17:02,750
He's talking upstairs.

351
00:17:04,790 --> 00:17:05,940
You are Sister Sheng Sheng

352
00:17:05,940 --> 00:17:07,110
that Mo Mo talks about, right?

353
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:10,270
I'm here to send Mo Mo her toy.

354
00:17:10,830 --> 00:17:11,630
She can't sleep

355
00:17:11,710 --> 00:17:12,630
without this toy

356
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:13,750
at night.

357
00:17:14,950 --> 00:17:16,180
You are such a good father.

358
00:17:17,590 --> 00:17:18,380
Children

359
00:17:18,750 --> 00:17:19,990
are precious to their parents.

360
00:17:31,870 --> 00:17:32,710
Why are you here?

361
00:17:34,390 --> 00:17:35,390
I'm here to visit Xiao Yi.

362
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:38,950
When did you come back?

363
00:17:40,110 --> 00:17:40,870
This morning.

364
00:17:47,910 --> 00:17:48,710
Sister.

365
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:51,910
Dad!

366
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:52,790
Mo Mo.

367
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,230
You are here.

368
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:55,430
Look what I brought you.

369
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:56,310
Come. I miss you.

370
00:17:56,340 --> 00:17:56,780
