371
00:17:58,790 --> 00:17:59,630
Do you miss me?

372
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:00,590
Yes.

373
00:18:01,910 --> 00:18:03,590
Sister, I want to eat strawberries.

374
00:18:04,950 --> 00:18:05,510
I'll go and wash them.

375
00:18:06,870 --> 00:18:08,190
Thank you.

376
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:10,070
Why is your daughter

377
00:18:10,110 --> 00:18:11,230
at Xiao Yi's house?

378
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:15,950
Mo Mo is Xiao Yi's sister.

379
00:18:16,190 --> 00:18:17,390
Can't she be here?

380
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:19,230
Xiao Yi is very busy.

381
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:21,470
You shouldn't trouble Xiao Yi with her.

382
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:24,390
Listen to you.

383
00:18:24,910 --> 00:18:25,750
How can it be troublesome

384
00:18:25,790 --> 00:18:26,630
when she's his sister?

385
00:18:27,150 --> 00:18:28,630
Why do you have to be so unpleasant?

386
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:30,430
I'm being unpleasant?

387
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:31,660
You've been

388
00:18:31,710 --> 00:18:32,830
troubling Xiao Yi for so many years.

389
00:18:32,980 --> 00:18:34,350
Do you want me to list them out?

390
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,950
You didn't trouble him.

391
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:39,950
You just ran away from him
as far as possible.

392
00:18:40,390 --> 00:18:41,550
Isn't it your fault that

393
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:42,660
Xiao Yi doesn't have a mother since young?

394
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:43,590
Nonsense!

395
00:18:44,310 --> 00:18:45,030
You've been asking Xiao Yi

396
00:18:45,470 --> 00:18:46,270
to pay for your family's living expenses

397
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:47,390
for so many years.

398
00:18:48,150 --> 00:18:49,670
Don't you feel ashamed?

399
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:51,230
What do you mean?

400
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:52,830
Xiao Yi doesn't

401
00:18:52,870 --> 00:18:53,430
want us to work.

402
00:18:53,470 --> 00:18:54,350
He's being filial.

403
00:18:54,910 --> 00:18:55,670
After so many years,

404
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:56,830
you are still

405
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:58,150
as shameless as before.

406
00:18:58,790 --> 00:18:59,390
If you are not shameless,

407
00:18:59,430 --> 00:19:00,470
why are you here?

408
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:02,390
You are getting old.

409
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:04,750
So, you want your son to support you now,

410
00:19:04,780 --> 00:19:05,190
right?

411
00:19:05,430 --> 00:19:06,630
Back then, you abandoned us,

412
00:19:06,670 --> 00:19:08,670
your burdens for your dream, right?

413
00:19:09,990 --> 00:19:11,030
I know

414
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:11,990
how much I owe Xiao Yi.

415
00:19:12,230 --> 00:19:13,230
But I'm not as greedy

416
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:14,670
as you are.

417
00:19:16,870 --> 00:19:17,390
Li Zhen.

418
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:19,030
Can you stop

419
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,150
acting so noble?

420
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:22,550
Mo Mo said that she found

421
00:19:22,670 --> 00:19:23,230
a lot of presents

422
00:19:23,260 --> 00:19:24,260
from you in Xiao Yi's room.

423
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,070
Xiao Yi has not opened any of them.

424
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:27,150
What does that mean?

425
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:28,710
It means that

426
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:29,980
he doesn't need your show of affection.

427
00:19:30,420 --> 00:19:31,950
Stop flattering yourself.

428
00:19:34,150 --> 00:19:35,430
I don't mind

429
00:19:35,590 --> 00:19:36,750
what Xiao Yi thinks of me.

430
00:19:37,390 --> 00:19:38,340
But let me warn you.

431
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:39,350
Xiao Yi is

432
00:19:39,390 --> 00:19:40,510
working hard for his career now.

433
00:19:40,950 --> 00:19:41,630
I won't allow you

434
00:19:41,710 --> 00:19:43,510
to burden him again and again.

435
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:46,630
One of us is burdening him

436
00:19:47,430 --> 00:19:48,110
and one of us abandoned him.

437
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:49,390
Great balance, right?

438
00:19:49,670 --> 00:19:50,150
Why are you...

439
00:19:50,190 --> 00:19:50,830
Enough!

440
00:20:01,190 --> 00:20:02,150
It's fine.

441
00:20:19,670 --> 00:20:21,190
Yi, you are free now?

442
00:20:22,710 --> 00:20:23,550
Why are you here?

443
00:20:23,950 --> 00:20:25,310
I came here to give something to Mo Mo.

444
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:29,470
Where is Yu Sheng Sheng?

445
00:20:30,910 --> 00:20:32,260
She went out just now.

446
00:20:32,790 --> 00:20:33,670
She left in a hurry.

447
00:20:33,710 --> 00:20:34,750
Maybe she has things to do.

448
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:37,590
Wait. Where are you going?

449
00:20:38,860 --> 00:20:39,670
I have things to do.

450
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:40,620
Keep them company.

451
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:42,790
Wear your cap and mask.

452
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:43,630
Okay.

453
00:20:46,670 --> 00:20:47,470
It'll fine, uncle, auntie.

454
00:20:47,630 --> 00:20:48,230
Don't worry.

455
00:20:48,470 --> 00:20:49,830
Take a seat.

456
00:20:49,860 --> 00:20:50,950
I'll make some tea for you.

457
00:20:51,790 --> 00:20:52,060
Okay.

458
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:53,310
Thank you.

459
00:20:56,870 --> 00:20:58,550
Come. Let's eat.

460
00:21:14,390 --> 00:21:15,550
[Where did he go?]

461
00:21:15,990 --> 00:21:17,260
[Why isn't he picking up the phone?]

462
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:21,550
[That's right.]

463
00:21:22,150 --> 00:21:23,630
[I have a tracking app in my phone.]

464
00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:17,590
Why are you here?

465
00:22:22,710 --> 00:22:23,470
Why are you here?

466
00:22:26,190 --> 00:22:27,020
Why didn't you pick up my call?

467
00:22:35,190 --> 00:22:35,870
I didn't hear you.

468
00:22:41,510 --> 00:22:41,830
Can you stop

469
00:22:41,870 --> 00:22:43,030
putting it in silent mode?

470
00:22:43,510 --> 00:22:43,790
I was

471
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:45,060
looking for you urgently.

472
00:22:48,230 --> 00:22:49,110
Jiang Da Chuan told me that

473
00:22:49,630 --> 00:22:50,830
your favourite Director Stephen

474
00:22:50,870 --> 00:22:51,750
wants to cast you in his movie.

475
00:22:51,950 --> 00:22:52,950
He asked me to go to Beijing tomorrow.

476
00:22:53,350 --> 00:22:54,150
How can I go?

477
00:22:54,470 --> 00:22:55,550
I'll ruin it.

478
00:22:57,270 --> 00:22:58,310
Go ahead and ruin it then.

479
00:22:59,070 --> 00:22:59,430
What?

480
00:23:04,470 --> 00:23:05,270
You are drinking?

481
00:23:10,470 --> 00:23:11,110
Stop it.

482
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:12,670
I have a bad tolerance to alcohol.

483
00:23:23,140 --> 00:23:23,710
Are you upset?

484
00:23:38,540 --> 00:23:39,270
Where are we?

485
00:23:40,390 --> 00:23:41,270
Why are you here?

486
00:23:46,430 --> 00:23:47,110
This is my home.

487
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:48,310
Your home?

488
00:23:53,790 --> 00:23:54,790
Your childhood home?

489
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:04,620
Are you reminded of
your unhappy childhood

490
00:24:04,670 --> 00:24:08,230
because your dad
met your mum today?

491
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:16,230
Go ahead and cry.

492
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:17,790
You are Yu Sheng Sheng now.

493
00:24:17,950 --> 00:24:18,830
I won't feel embarrassed.

494
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,030
I've cried enough

495
00:24:29,070 --> 00:24:30,150
when I was young.

496
00:24:33,870 --> 00:24:35,030
I don't want to cry for them anymore.

497
00:24:37,790 --> 00:24:38,830
[Let's file a divorce then.]

498
00:24:39,470 --> 00:24:40,750
[Do you think I can't live without you?]

499
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,750
If you didn't stop me

500
00:24:43,990 --> 00:24:44,750
and always demoralise me,

501
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:46,100
I would've been successful.

502
00:24:46,950 --> 00:24:47,630
Jiang Dong Hai.

503
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:50,230
Why can't you see that

504
00:24:50,270 --> 00:24:52,190
your so-called business is so unreliable?

505
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:54,430
How would I know if
I didn't give it a try?

506
00:24:54,630 --> 00:24:55,510
Just like your experiment.

507
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:56,350
Did you conduct an experiment

508
00:24:56,350 --> 00:24:57,100
because you know that it'll be successful?

509
00:24:57,150 --> 00:24:58,230
They are not the same!

510
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,230
What do you mean?

511
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:00,710
Your work is your dream

512
00:25:00,870 --> 00:25:02,230
and my work is considered as daydreaming?

513
00:25:08,150 --> 00:25:09,830
Can you drink less

514
00:25:10,390 --> 00:25:12,110
and find a proper job?

515
00:25:12,830 --> 00:25:15,070
Stop reaching for something
beyond your grasp.

516
00:25:15,990 --> 00:25:16,580
I've said it before.

517
00:25:16,990 --> 00:25:18,030
I don't need you to teach me.

518
00:25:18,630 --> 00:25:20,190
I'm not trying to teach you.

519
00:25:20,630 --> 00:25:21,790
I'm just worried that if this continues,

520
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:23,350
you won't be able to take care of Xiao Yi.

521
00:25:26,510 --> 00:25:27,750
So, you've already decided

522
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:28,830
to leave Xiao Yi with me.

523
00:25:29,590 --> 00:25:31,190
Li Zhen, you are amazing, right?

524
00:25:31,430 --> 00:25:32,830
Bring Xiao Yi with you abroad.

525
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,550
I'll be very busy over there.

526
00:25:34,630 --> 00:25:36,830
I won't have time to take care of him.

527
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:38,700
Besides, it'll be better to let him

528
00:25:38,950 --> 00:25:40,020
stay here.

529
00:25:40,230 --> 00:25:41,150
I'm busy too.

530
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:42,660
What about my career?

531
00:25:42,910 --> 00:25:44,230
What career do you have?

532
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,390
Jiang Dong Hai.

533
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:47,590
You are so free.

534
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:50,140
Can you contribute to this family?

535
00:25:50,430 --> 00:25:52,110
Can you be like a man?

536
00:25:52,630 --> 00:25:53,870
I'm not acting like a man.

537
00:25:53,870 --> 00:25:54,910
And you are not acting like a woman.

538
00:25:55,110 --> 00:25:55,990
Xiao Yi is still so young.

539
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:56,950
And you want to abandon him

540
00:25:56,990 --> 00:25:57,790
to go abroad.

541
00:25:58,150 --> 00:25:59,350
You are so cruel.

542
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,550
I've told you many times.

543
00:26:03,590 --> 00:26:04,350
This is a rare opportunity

544
00:26:04,390 --> 00:26:05,790
for me to work abroad.

545
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:06,830
Say no more.

546
00:26:06,980 --> 00:26:08,110
This is the truth.

547
00:26:09,910 --> 00:26:11,190
You don't want to take care of Xiao Yi.

548
00:26:27,550 --> 00:26:27,910
Come.

549
00:26:28,910 --> 00:26:29,590
Be careful.

550
00:26:30,150 --> 00:26:30,790
Walk slowly.

551
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:34,470
I already told you that
I have bad tolerance to alcohol.

552
00:26:34,670 --> 00:26:35,830
Why did you have to drink so much?

553
00:26:35,950 --> 00:26:36,710
I didn't.

554
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:42,030
Look. An aeroplane.

555
00:26:42,470 --> 00:26:43,950
Yes. A huge aeroplane.

556
00:26:50,310 --> 00:26:50,870
What's wrong?

557
00:27:00,950 --> 00:27:01,790
It's so late already.

558
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:03,470
Let's take a taxi to go home, okay?

559
00:27:06,350 --> 00:27:07,230
I don't have a home.

560
00:27:11,670 --> 00:27:12,110
Look.

561
00:27:14,310 --> 00:27:15,670
Look at the myriad of twinkling lights.

562
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:18,910
They are so bright.

563
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:22,460
But none of them

564
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:23,510
belongs to me.

565
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,830
None of them wants me.

566
00:27:33,870 --> 00:27:35,190
No one wants me.

567
00:27:36,270 --> 00:27:36,950
Why are you like a child

568
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,150
when you are drunk?

569
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:42,630
Let's get up first, okay?

570
00:27:43,510 --> 00:27:44,870
None of them wants me.

571
00:27:45,990 --> 00:27:47,070
No one wants me.

572
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:48,310
That's not true.

573
00:27:48,710 --> 00:27:49,310
I want you.

574
00:27:49,950 --> 00:27:50,710
You are so good.

575
00:27:50,870 --> 00:27:53,470
I want to put you in my arms,

576
00:27:53,910 --> 00:27:54,990
take care of you

577
00:27:55,110 --> 00:27:56,310
and treat you like the apple of my eye.

578
00:27:58,220 --> 00:27:59,230
Let's go home, okay?

579
00:28:01,510 --> 00:28:02,310
How am I good?

580
00:28:10,980 --> 00:28:11,390
Look.

581
00:28:12,110 --> 00:28:13,070
There are so many street lights here.

582
00:28:13,620 --> 00:28:14,310
